sing telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Their shells are very durable. Even if they crack, they can survive without spilling their contents."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Using telepathy only they can employ, they always form a cluster of six EXEGGCUTE."},{"version":"black","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"white","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"x","text":"Its six eggs converse using telepathy. They can quickly gather if they become separated."},{"version":"y","text":"Even though it appears to be eggs of some sort, it was discovered to be a life-form more like plant seeds."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its six eggs use telepathy to communicate among themselves. It is believed to carry plant genes and the genes of other species."},{"version":"moon","text":"Six of them together form a full-fledged Pok\u00e9mon. It\u2019s often hunted by Crabrawler, but uses psychokinesis to drive it off."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Six of them form a single Pok\u00e9mon. Should one of the six be lost, the next morning there will once more be six."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Although they are the same size as other Exeggcute, the ones produced in Alola are quite heavy. Their shells are packed full."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"The heads attract each other and spin around. There must be six heads for it to maintain balance."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"The heads attract each other and spin around. There must be six heads for it to maintain balance."},{"version":"sword","text":"Though it may look like it\u2019s just a bunch of eggs, it\u2019s a proper Pok\u00e9mon. Exeggcute communicates with others of its kind via telepathy, apparently."},{"version":"shield","text":"These Pok\u00e9mon get nervous when they\u2019re not in a group of six. The minute even one member of the group goes missing, Exeggcute become cowardly."}],"evo":{"name":"exeggcute","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"exeggutor","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"leaf-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/102.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/102.png","capture":90,"happiness":70,"growth":"slow","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"defense":1},"forms":[]}